    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sun-dried tomato pesto</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> – this is your<strong> pesto stock</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1675.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1675.-step-3-x400.jpg",
