            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> from the pan (keep the orzo cooking!) and transfer it to a clean board, then shred it apart using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
