    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is tender, add most of the <strong>grated cheese </strong>(save some for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> red pepper & pesto orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more water if your pan is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
